    public abstract class AbstractEvaluator
extends java.lang.Object
implements InputEvaluator
    ensures for the supported primitive types that they hold an appropriate format. Some of the evaluation engines do not support this (e.g. they return a 1.0 as an integer, which breaks the integer parsing).

    Felix Dobslaw
